{"article_id":"AmQoGb4HEMEUBgXu","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump signaled Thursday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that he will likely declare a national emergency","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to have the military build his border wall","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"unless Congress negotiates a deal","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"to give him the money .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"As he departed the White House en route to Texas for a visit to the border","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"he said","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"it \" would be very surprising to me \"","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"if he didn ' t go that route ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"should talks on Capitol Hill continue to stall .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"\" I have the absolute right","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"to declare a national emergency , \"","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"\" If this doesn ' t work out ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"probably I will do it .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"I would almost say definitely . \"","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"He also tamped down on a report","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"that steel bollard fencing was easily penetrated during tests of the wall prototypes","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"the president had built in 2017 .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"\" The wall","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"that we ' re doing","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"is very , very hard to penetrate , \"","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"he said .","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"With the partial government shutdown now at the end of its third week , Mr. Trump has increasingly focused on tapping his powers under the National Emergencies Act and other sections of law","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"to task the military with carrying out his border wall plans .","depth":4},{"id":25,"text":"Democrats have vowed legal challenges ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"though legal analysts have been skeptical","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"those will ultimately succeed .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"A bigger threat could be opposition from Republicans","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"who say","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"the military doesn ' t have the spare money","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"to devote billions of dollars to fence construction .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Mr. Trump , though , said","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"there is a \" tremendous amount of funds \"","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"he could use .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"The president said","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"he ' s not yet prepared to go the emergency route ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"but said","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"his lawyers have told him","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"the law does grant him the powers","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"he would need .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"He had called congressional leaders to the White House Wednesday for a round of negotiations","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"but walked out","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"after House Speaker Nancy Pelosi said","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"she will never approve money for any wall .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Mr. Trump disputed Democrats ' claims","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"that he threw a \" temper tantrum . \"","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"\" I didn ' t pound my table ,","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"I didn ' t raise my voice , \"","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"He also blasted reporters for what he said","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"were biased reports and distortions ,","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"\" 80 percent of you are possibly in coordination with the opposition party . \"","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"President Obama had called the border a \" crisis \"","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"and said","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"Democrats have voted for fencing in the past ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"only to oppose it now .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":117,"left":81,"right":116,"rel